<bibRefCitation author="Mongkolsuk P &amp; Meesim S &amp; Poengsungnoen V &amp; Buaruang K &amp; Schumm F &amp; Kalb K" box="[229,485,665,689]" pageId="8" pageNumber="1429" pagination="1 - 66" refId="ref8243" refString="Mongkolsuk P, Meesim S, Poengsungnoen V, Buaruang K, Schumm F, Kalb K (2015) The lichen family Physciaceae in Thailand - II. Contributions to the genus Heterodermia sensu lato. Phytotaxa 235 (1): 1 - 66. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / phytotaxa. 235.1.1" type="journal article" year="2015">Mongkolsuk et al. 2015</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Diaz-Escandon D" box="[496,722,665,689]" pageId="8" pageNumber="1429" refId="ref7800" refString="Diaz-Escandon D (2017) La tribu Heterodermieae Trevis. en Colombia. Master tesis, Universidad del Valle, Cali, 115 pp." type="book" year="2017">Díaz-Escandón 2017</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
